Package: air
Type: Package
Title: AI help to write and understand R code
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Soumya",
           family = "Ray",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "soumya.ray@gmail.com")
Description: An R console utility that lets you ask R related questions to 
    OpenAI's large language model. It can answer "how-to" questions by directly 
    providing code, and "whatis" questions by explaining what given code does.
    You must provision your own OpenAI API key.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    httr,
    keyring,
    rjson
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    vcr (>= 0.6.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
